definitions.definition: A dish of glass or earthenware , with a lid , in which food is baked and sometimes served .
Food, such as a stew , cooked in such a dish.
Any type of food that fills the high-walled dish or pan in which it was cooked. (Can we add an example for this sense?)

main_definition: ( countable ) A dish of glass or earthenware , with a lid , in which food is baked and sometimes served .
secondary_definitions: Food, such as a stew , cooked in such a dish.
( by extension ) Any type of food that fills the high-walled dish or pan in which it was cooked. (Can we add an example for this sense?)
